summary: gets rid of the mouth box on Female humans
descriptionHtml:
[line]
[size=7][center]INFO[/center][/size]
[list][size=6]
[*]Gets Rid of The Black Mouth Box for Human Females
[*]Its If you see a Black texture on the side of your characters face jaw area, my characters jaw is a bit more narrow than normal so this is a great fix
[*]No Other Required Mods (StandAlone)
[*]Will Remove TEETH!!!!!!! ITS MORE FOR SCREEN SHOTS
[/size][/list]

[center][size=3]To install, just download with the NMM, then Activate it. If you like this mod Please share it with a Friend, It helps alot.
